snippet.title: Help! I'm Haunted Trailer
snippet.description:
HELP! I’M HAUNTED is a 2D platformer about busting ghosts in Neo-Transylvania, upgrading your unlicensed arsenal to battle a crew of monsters led by Dr. Victor Frankenstein.
